Cleaning stages. 1a: * Remove useless columns * Done in python scripts (Reddit/main and Twitter/main)

1b: * Remove any anomalies/useless posts missed by filters (e.g. blanks/removed/NaN, etc.) * All lower-case. * Tokenize * Noise removal (punctuation, special characters, stopwords).

2: * Stemming

  mutate(man_sentiment = as.factor(man_sentiment),
         bing_score = as.factor(bing_score), 
         afinn_score = as.factor(afinn_score),
         nrc_score = as.factor(nrc_score))

  filter(man_sentiment != 0) %>% 
  mutate(man_sentiment = as.factor(man_sentiment),
         bing_score = as.factor(bing_score),
         afinn_score = as.factor(afinn_score),
